                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Personalized Discovery</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Create an intelligent music discovery system that helps users find new music they'll love.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Modern Interface</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Design a clean, modern dark-themed UI that's perfect for extended listening sessions.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 18h.01M8 21h8a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Cross-Platform Experience</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Ensure seamless experience across web, mobile, desktop, smart speakers, and car systems.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Challenges -->
        <section class="py-16 bg-white">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-8">
                    <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-green-600 mr-4"></div>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Challenges</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <div class="flex items-start bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
                        <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mr-4">
                            <span class="text-white font-bold">1</span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Real-Time Music Recommendations</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">Building an AI system that learns user preferences and provides accurate, engaging music recommendations in real-time.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
                        <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mr-4">
                            <span class="text-white font-bold">2</span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Managing Huge Content Libraries</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">Handling millions of songs, podcasts, and playlists with efficient search and instant access.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
                        <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mr-4">
                            <span class="text-white font-bold">3</span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Uniform Design Across Platforms</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">Maintaining consistent brand experience and functionality across diverse devices and operating systems.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Solution -->
        <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-gray-100">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-8">
                    <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-green-600 mr-4"></div>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Our Solution</h2>
                </div>
                
                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg mb-8">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Strategic Analysis</h3>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="flex items-start">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                            </svg>
                            <p class="text-gray-700">Personalization drives user retention - users stay longer when they discover music they love.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                            </svg>
                            <p class="text-gray-700">Dark-themed UI improves long session comfort and reduces eye strain during extended listening.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                            </svg>
                            <p class="text-gray-700">Smart caching and adaptive streaming reduce buffering and data usage significantly.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Implementation Approach</h3>
                    <div class="space-y-6">
                        <div class="border-l-4 border-green-600 pl-6">
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Fast, Lightweight Frontend</h4>
                            <p class="text-gray-700">Built with optimized React components ensuring instant navigation and minimal resource consumption across all devices.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-6">
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">AI-Powered Recommendations</h4>
                            <p class="text-gray-700">Implemented Discover Weekly, Release Radar, and Daily Mix using machine learning algorithms that analyze listening patterns.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-600 pl-6">
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Scalable Backend</h4>
                            <p class="text-gray-700">Microservices architecture handling billions of streams with real-time analytics and instant playback initiation.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="border-l-4 border-orange-600 pl-6">
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Adaptive Streaming Technology</h4>
                            <p class="text-gray-700">Smart bitrate adjustment based on network conditions ensuring smooth playback without interruptions.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Results -->
        <section class="py-16 bg-white">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-8">
                    <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-green-600 mr-4"></div>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Results & Impact</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
                    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-green-100 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
                        <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">25%</div>
                        <div class="text-gray-700 font-semibold">Increase in Listening Time</div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Users spend more time on platform discovering new music</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-blue-100 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
                        <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">350M+</div>
                        <div class="text-gray-700 font-semibold">Active Users</div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Global user base across all platforms</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-purple-100 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
