                            <span>Faster onboarding process using social login integration</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                            </svg>
                            <span>Industry-leading music discovery with AI-powered playlists</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                            </svg>
                            <span>Cross-platform synchronization allowing seamless device switching</span>
